data.description: Beautiful Home 2021 NEW CONSTRUCTION NO HOA ....3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms sitting in 1.59 acres UPLAND lot. This property, boasting high-end finishes, is situated in a perfect location in the fast-growing area of Golden Gate Estates. tile throughout gorgeous tray ceilings, and A/C at the garage. But there is even more: Ceiling Fans, foam insulation, cooktop, wall-mounted oven and microwave, controlled garage door, central AC water heater everything is brand new and ...Ready for you to move in... Deep lot with plenty of space for a future pool. You do not need to pay for water have a well. Owners are very motivated Great for trucks a lot of space to park your trucks. Please call for an appointment Please Don't Bother the owners.
